Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾有互相憎恨之人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.57,0:00:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍腐於野 血染英魂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.07,0:00:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羈絆斷於利刃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.24,0:00:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心在黑暗中哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.84,0:00:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心愛之人 且赴黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了 陽炎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.44,0:03:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 您作何打算 弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.81,0:03:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙目如此狀況 駿府之行…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.97,0:03:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此行旨在一探家康大人的真意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.48,0:03:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若未達成此事 怎可折回
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊賀人的襲擊早在意料之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此便畏縮不前 終究難達駿府
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是屬下杞人憂天了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.42,0:03:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待左衛門歸來 我們就啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好出發的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.89,0:03:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.17,0:04:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若真是杞人憂天就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.37,0:04:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條路 不能回頭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.79,0:04:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是修羅之途
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.74,0:04:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,念鬼閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方纔你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.10,0:04:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說高興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.62,0:04:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為弦之介等人已命喪我手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了甲賀弦之介？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法使用瞳術的他不是對手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,0:05:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室賀豹馬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.89,0:05:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對付盲目的忍者 易如反掌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敗於你的蝴蝶 灰頭土臉回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫陽炎的女人 我也順便收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 如月左衛門呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺憾之至
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜唯有他一人漏網
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這有失念鬼閣下作風
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.39,0:05:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.77,0:05:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著嗎 如月左衛門
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.67,0:05:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.11,0:05:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽炎臨終前坦白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.56,0:05:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死夜叉丸的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:06:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是如月左衛門
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,念鬼閣下這等人物 怎會如此大意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如月左衛門
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.35,0:06:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那傢伙把夜叉丸閣下…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,念鬼閣下放走誰都不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.89,0:06:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該先收拾那個左衛門的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這或許是天意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:07:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓我親手處決如月左衛門
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你殺得了他嗎 螢火
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人的臉不知道會變成什麼人的樣子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論左衛門變成誰 我都不會認錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.27,0:07:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.95,0:08:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然能識破
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,識破我嗎 螢火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.48,0:09:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如…月…左衛門…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.02,0:09:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜叉丸…閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.07,0:10:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜…叉丸…閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜…叉…丸…閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.29,0:11:51.61,name,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\pos(828,30)\frz-90}桑名渡口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼非要跑來坐船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏挑海路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要渡過七里汪洋 簡直要我的命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陣五郎閣下 您如此討厭海嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.44,0:12:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用問
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.82,0:12:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這溶於鹽的身體若浸到海水會怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.65,0:12:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是想想 就渾身抖個不停
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別抱怨了 陣五郎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們又不是游過去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.94,0:12:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊 害怕的東西就是怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近 沒有發現甲賀人用船的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.07,0:13:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們取道陸路的佐屋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.85,0:13:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們乘船便可超過他們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 天膳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,念鬼和螢火還未歸來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們真的就這樣登船而去？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間等待不歸之人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.60,0:13:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今還未現身 便可說明一切了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.82,0:14:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出船嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下雖不好爭鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但亦不會躲避汝等追擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.64,0:14:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲賀五人 伊賀七人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.85,0:14:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大可在疾行途中施展忍法相鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.34,0:14:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊賀七人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人已將我算入剩下的七名敵人之一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明知內情故意設下圈套
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.97,0:14:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他必是這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.67,0:15:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想他知道並非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.24,0:15:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.13,0:15:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請小心 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四郎 你陪著我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來您在這裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.98,0:15:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危險的 來 進船艙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.30,0:15:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次乘船出行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.26,0:15:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少感受一下海潮的味道也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.22,0:15:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎 朱絹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海潮的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:15:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波浪的喧音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海鳥的鳴聲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘是初次經歷之事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.72,0:16:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓各位見笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獻醜了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害 都聽入迷了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.62,0:17:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一曲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 就是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.55,0:17:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱絹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.09,0:17:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.21,0:17:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帶著陣五郎去船尾的房間好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船尾的房間？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有話想和朧小姐單獨談
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.19,0:17:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這期間 不要讓任何人到船腹來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫小四郎把守
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:17:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要他坐在那裏 人們就會怕得不敢接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.09,0:18:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以是可以 但是您要對朧小姐說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船這麼直奔宮渡口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許立即會與甲賀一方交手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而關鍵的朧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.42,0:18:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻貌似心不在焉的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在讓人放心不下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.11,0:18:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁船上之時 摸清朧小姐的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何務必請她下定決心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.85,0:18:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.34,0:18:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天膳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.92,0:18:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.21,0:18:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如朧小姐不肯的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.94,0:19:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.53,0:19:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無需擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧小姐會聽的 一定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.99,0:19:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話 真是美妙的笛聲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一點沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一會兒給他們送壺酒去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.83,0:19:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.16,0:20:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要多久才到宮渡口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.89,0:20:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 朱絹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天膳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天膳 朱絹他們去哪裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.05,0:21:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱絹和陣五郎在船尾的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.63,0:21:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.82,0:21:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天膳？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.75,0:21:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在下有話要對您說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.40,0:23:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化為不共戴天的因緣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.19,0:23:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 沉浸於幽邃回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.41,0:23:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相思難斷的是少女的悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.76,0:23:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踐踏主從律儀迫近的凌辱魔手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.28,0:23:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲痛的呼叫震撼浪潮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.84,0:23:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烙印在矛盾的鼓膜上的悲鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.81,0:23:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逼迫忍者作出抉擇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.40,0:24:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 Basilisk 甲賀忍法帖

